WEBVTT

00:23.930 --> 00:24.640
Tell me,

00:25.470 --> 00:27.430
what exactly is Blood on Snow?

00:28.600 --> 00:30.260
What you make me take each time

00:30.510 --> 00:32.509
only temporarily relieves my pain,

00:32.790 --> 00:34.720
but worsens the poison in my blood.

00:37.470 --> 00:40.200
The renowned General Zhuge of Great Yong

00:40.430 --> 00:42.560
and the future heir of Qingshan Manor

00:42.560 --> 00:44.420
truly lives up to his reputation.

00:45.000 --> 00:46.070
Not only did you escape alive

00:46.070 --> 00:48.240
from my heavily guarded Li'an City,

00:48.240 --> 00:51.040
but you also managed
to stand here threatening me.

00:53.390 --> 00:55.350
Give me the antidote for Blood on Snow.

00:55.350 --> 00:57.150
Don't try to control me anymore.

00:57.200 --> 00:59.000
Let me go,

00:59.320 --> 01:01.030
and I'll get it for you.

01:04.349 --> 01:05.870
The antidote for Blood on Snow

01:05.870 --> 01:08.150
is the most precious antidote in Ximeng.

01:08.150 --> 01:10.280
No one possesses it except me.

01:10.760 --> 01:11.920
If you kill me,

01:13.560 --> 01:16.230
you will never get it.

01:18.950 --> 01:20.000
Go get it now.

01:20.920 --> 01:21.920
I will go with you.

01:23.200 --> 01:24.200
Alright.

01:43.479 --> 01:44.150
Zhuge Yue!

01:44.789 --> 01:46.200
If you still want to live,

01:46.220 --> 01:47.210
put the blade down!

01:47.210 --> 01:48.210
Then let's see

01:49.039 --> 01:50.039
who is faster.

01:57.700 --> 01:58.710
Stop!

02:03.640 --> 02:05.240
Since you like making deals,

02:06.200 --> 02:07.530
let's make another one.

02:07.840 --> 02:09.560
You did save me at Mount Ximin

02:09.910 --> 02:11.590
and gave me Bone-Chilling Grass.

02:11.590 --> 02:13.120
So, I'll do 3 things for you,

02:13.470 --> 02:16.110
and in return, you give me the antidote
for Blood on Snow and let me go.

02:16.110 --> 02:18.170
The Battle of Li'an was the first one.

02:18.710 --> 02:19.710
And now,

02:21.150 --> 02:22.280
there are 2 left.

02:25.000 --> 02:25.630
Alright!

02:26.650 --> 02:27.740
It's a deal.

03:50.680 --> 03:55.470
[REBIRTH]

03:55.840 --> 03:58.450
[Episode 9]

04:17.870 --> 04:18.600
Who's there?

04:19.240 --> 04:20.170
Don't be afraid.

04:21.040 --> 04:23.870
I didn't light the lamp
to avoid drawing attention.

04:23.870 --> 04:24.920
Like them,

04:25.310 --> 04:26.570
I work for the Empress.

04:27.070 --> 04:28.360
You are all spies,

04:29.240 --> 04:30.440
so why did you save me?

04:32.800 --> 04:34.870
No one is born a spy.

04:35.190 --> 04:35.870
Besides,

04:36.070 --> 04:38.000
I've known you from the beginning.

04:38.430 --> 04:41.270
My father was a defending general
of Hongchuan City,

04:41.270 --> 04:42.430
whose surname was Mu.

04:42.430 --> 04:45.360
He fought against the Great Yong army
alongside you.

04:45.720 --> 04:47.320
That was when I first saw you.

05:01.360 --> 05:01.760
You...

05:01.990 --> 05:02.870
You are lying!

05:03.040 --> 05:05.000
I remember every soldier
who died in battle

05:05.000 --> 05:06.060
at Hongchuan City.

05:06.350 --> 05:07.950
None of them was surnamed Mu.

05:08.920 --> 05:09.700
You're the one

05:09.700 --> 05:11.450
who slipped into my room that day,
aren't you?

05:11.450 --> 05:15.300
[Boque Palace]

05:12.950 --> 05:15.150
It's a long way from the main courtyard.

05:15.750 --> 05:17.550
Your companions can't hear you,

05:17.900 --> 05:19.630
and they won't come to save you.

05:20.510 --> 05:23.190
So you'd better tell me exactly

05:23.600 --> 05:25.830
what you reported to the Empress.

05:31.390 --> 05:32.230
That's right.

05:33.360 --> 05:35.159
I'm the one who went into her room

05:35.480 --> 05:37.280
and found the Xiuli Army's flag.

05:37.430 --> 05:39.090
But I didn't tell Her Majesty,

05:39.520 --> 05:42.190
because I wanted to kill her myself.

05:42.830 --> 05:44.290
It's the Empress's order?

05:49.190 --> 05:51.120
I'm the one who wants her dead.

05:51.720 --> 05:54.920
My father's name was Mu Zheng.

05:55.950 --> 05:59.680
He was an imperial guard commander
in Zhenhuang City of Great Yong.

05:59.800 --> 06:02.870
But because Chu Qiao
and Heir Apparent Yan rebelled,

06:03.600 --> 06:05.330
my entire family was executed.

06:06.230 --> 06:08.690
My mother sacrificed her life
to protect me.

06:09.030 --> 06:11.740
I hate Chu Qiao. I hate the Xiuli Army.

06:12.310 --> 06:13.410
As long as I'm alive,

06:13.410 --> 06:14.940
I will try to kill her again.

06:15.480 --> 06:16.680
If you want to kill me,

06:17.070 --> 06:18.270
do it now.

06:19.070 --> 06:20.510
Since you won't talk...

06:22.310 --> 06:22.970
Song Cheng.

06:23.420 --> 06:23.950
Yes.

06:34.630 --> 06:35.390
Let her go.

06:36.560 --> 06:37.240
Qiao.

06:38.120 --> 06:40.720
If you let her go,
she will try to kill you again.

06:48.510 --> 06:49.430
Then let her.

06:50.480 --> 06:52.510
Do you think by doing this,

06:52.909 --> 06:54.710
I'll be grateful to you

06:54.730 --> 06:56.610
and be loyal to you like a dog?

06:57.310 --> 06:59.480
Your whole family died tragically
because of me.

06:59.480 --> 07:01.340
It's only right for you to hate me.

07:02.270 --> 07:03.270
You are not wrong.

07:03.950 --> 07:05.480
You are not the one to blame.

07:23.120 --> 07:23.800
Go.

07:30.630 --> 07:32.390
You will regret letting me go.

07:32.950 --> 07:34.550
Then before I change my mind,

07:35.390 --> 07:36.270
get out of here.

07:41.190 --> 07:42.650
Has Minglu been sent back?

07:44.950 --> 07:46.830
I also had Song Cheng
prepare medicine for her,

07:46.830 --> 07:47.630
but she didn't take it.

07:47.630 --> 07:48.890
She left it in the room.

07:49.040 --> 07:50.300
How are your injuries?

07:50.310 --> 07:51.040
It's fine.

07:51.430 --> 07:53.560
The illness I caught in the frozen lake

07:53.560 --> 07:55.760
flared up while I was in the water today.

07:56.120 --> 07:56.870
Otherwise,

07:57.510 --> 08:00.910
Minglu and her companions
wouldn't have been able to hurt me.

08:01.360 --> 08:02.000
Qiao,

08:02.720 --> 08:03.850
don't overthink it.

08:03.950 --> 08:05.750
Minglu's fate is not your fault.

08:06.390 --> 08:08.510
You were just temporarily blinded
by Yan Xun,

08:08.510 --> 08:09.600
which is why you helped him.

08:09.600 --> 08:11.130
I was not blinded by Yan Xun.

08:11.300 --> 08:12.560
I knew what I was doing.

08:20.990 --> 08:23.160
You've never lived in Zhenhuang City,

08:24.080 --> 08:25.560
nor do you know what it feels like

08:25.560 --> 08:26.680
to be a slave.

08:28.120 --> 08:30.420
Slaves don't deserve
to have their own names.

08:30.420 --> 08:31.760
Even when they are sick or injured,

08:31.760 --> 08:33.620
they can't be treated by a doctor.

08:34.080 --> 08:36.510
Not only are their own lives
treated like dirt,

08:36.510 --> 08:38.130
but the lives of their companions
and siblings

08:38.130 --> 08:40.460
are also held in the hands
of the nobility.

08:40.480 --> 08:42.840
If Yan Xun and I
hadn't rebelled back then,

08:43.480 --> 08:44.510
I'm afraid that

08:45.550 --> 08:46.600
in Zhenhuang City now,

08:46.600 --> 08:48.750
only our corpses would be left.

08:51.480 --> 08:53.990
I was worried
that you'd be sad and blame yourself.

08:53.990 --> 08:55.590
It seems I was overthinking.

08:58.160 --> 08:59.890
I wasn't helping Yan Xun rebel.

09:02.840 --> 09:03.960
I just believe

09:04.790 --> 09:07.050
that there should be a place in this world

09:07.320 --> 09:08.720
where everyone is equal.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.000
Qiao,

09:12.510 --> 09:13.510
you are too brave.

09:14.360 --> 09:15.000
But...

09:15.630 --> 09:16.630
I have a question.

09:17.630 --> 09:19.270
If one day

09:19.270 --> 09:21.870
you really create
a great harmonious society,

09:22.000 --> 09:23.600
could you keep a place for me?

09:23.960 --> 09:24.960
My requirements are not high.

09:24.960 --> 09:27.240
The place must be bigger than Zhuge Yue's.

09:27.240 --> 09:29.200
After all, I am more handsome

09:29.320 --> 09:30.850
and more humorous than him.

09:32.360 --> 09:34.820
Can this land be distributed
based on looks?

09:35.510 --> 09:36.550
It's fair, right?

09:37.960 --> 09:39.240
Distributed by looks?

09:45.790 --> 09:46.790
Are you sure

09:47.720 --> 09:49.980
you can get a bigger place than Zhuge Yue?

09:50.360 --> 09:51.150
Qiao,

09:51.840 --> 09:52.510
it's not that I want to criticize you.

09:52.510 --> 09:53.720
You're good at everything,

09:53.720 --> 09:55.790
but your taste is so...

09:59.790 --> 10:00.440
Oh, right.

10:01.360 --> 10:04.030
If Minglu wasn't the one
who tipped off the Empress,

10:04.030 --> 10:05.960
then how did your identity get leaked?

10:05.960 --> 10:06.720
Mother

10:07.570 --> 10:09.090
seems very certain

10:09.750 --> 10:10.950
that you are Chu Qiao.

10:11.670 --> 10:13.670
There is another person in Biantang

10:14.270 --> 10:16.070
who knows my identity very well.

10:17.000 --> 10:17.530
Who is it?

10:20.320 --> 10:21.650
The envoy of Great Yong,

10:22.240 --> 10:23.150
Zhao Kuo.

10:34.820 --> 10:36.610
[Tangjing]

10:35.180 --> 10:35.820
Lord Zhao!

10:38.120 --> 10:38.750
My Lord!

10:39.550 --> 10:40.390
The wind is too strong tonight.

10:40.390 --> 10:42.480
Why don't we wait until tomorrow
to set off?

10:42.480 --> 10:43.840
The messenger we sent

10:43.840 --> 10:44.790
hasn't returned yet.

10:44.790 --> 10:46.840
He must have died
at the hands of Chu Qiao.

10:46.840 --> 10:48.440
If we keep staying in Biantang,

10:48.440 --> 10:49.810
there will surely be trouble.

10:49.810 --> 10:50.870
Now we must go back immediately

10:50.870 --> 10:52.130
to report to Lord Muhe.

10:52.160 --> 10:52.840
Let's go!

10:59.320 --> 11:00.390
Help!

11:00.510 --> 11:02.770
Princess Fu was poisoned and passed out!

11:03.720 --> 11:04.320
Move!

11:09.780 --> 11:10.640
Your Highness.

11:13.670 --> 11:15.270
Fu? Fu?

11:19.070 --> 11:19.930
What happened?

11:20.320 --> 11:21.180
Your Highness,

11:21.320 --> 11:23.780
there's something wrong with the pastries.

11:27.130 --> 11:28.460
Someone poisoned them.

11:28.800 --> 11:30.660
Drive all those concubines away!

11:31.150 --> 11:32.030
Your Highness,

11:32.150 --> 11:32.910
you can't go in!

11:32.910 --> 11:34.640
Her Majesty is already asleep.

11:34.790 --> 11:35.670
Your Highness!

11:36.570 --> 11:38.510
Your Highness, you can't go in!

11:38.510 --> 11:39.390
Your Highness!

11:39.390 --> 11:40.320
Your Highness,

11:40.760 --> 11:42.080
Her Majesty is not feeling well

11:42.080 --> 11:42.790
and has already gone to sleep.

11:42.790 --> 11:44.670
I need to see Her Majesty
for something important.

11:44.670 --> 11:47.130
Your Highness, please wait until tomorrow!

11:47.600 --> 11:48.460
Your Highness!

11:50.870 --> 11:51.750
Crown Prince.

11:53.000 --> 11:55.130
You are becoming more and more unruly.

11:56.320 --> 11:58.480
Do you know what the punishment is

11:59.200 --> 12:01.530
for breaking into the harem late at night?

12:13.630 --> 12:14.890
Protect His Lordship!

12:28.320 --> 12:29.340
Chu Qiao?

12:31.000 --> 12:31.480
Go!

12:45.160 --> 12:45.960
Kill her!

13:09.510 --> 13:10.270
Chu Qiao!

13:10.820 --> 13:12.470
Your martial arts have been restored?

13:12.470 --> 13:13.600
I am no match for you!

13:14.320 --> 13:15.600
B-But your

13:15.600 --> 13:17.390
relentless pursuit of killing me today

13:17.390 --> 13:19.090
is simply because
you're afraid I'll expose your identity,

13:19.090 --> 13:21.510
and you'll no longer be able to pretend
to be Princess Fu of Biantang.

13:21.510 --> 13:22.320
I admit it!

13:22.790 --> 13:23.590
It was me.

13:23.610 --> 13:25.170
I was the one who reported you
to the Biantang Empress.

13:25.170 --> 13:27.320
But now I have information
to trade with you!

13:27.320 --> 13:28.120
Spare my life,

13:28.600 --> 13:29.600
and we'll be even.

13:31.630 --> 13:32.490
The Xiuli Army.

13:33.530 --> 13:34.720
Your Xiuli Army!

13:37.390 --> 13:38.320
What did you say?

13:38.910 --> 13:41.030
He Xiao from the Xiuli Army—

13:41.660 --> 13:42.660
he is not dead!

13:48.240 --> 13:49.700
Princess Fu was poisoned?

13:50.450 --> 13:51.650
When did this happen?

13:51.720 --> 13:52.360
Mother,

13:53.270 --> 13:55.120
are you still pretending not to know?

13:55.120 --> 13:57.080
Just now, 2 hours ago,

13:57.270 --> 13:59.240
someone poisoned Princess Fu's pastries.

13:59.240 --> 14:00.700
She is still unconscious.

14:00.880 --> 14:02.480
Even if you suspect Fu's identity

14:02.480 --> 14:03.940
and fear she might harm me,

14:04.170 --> 14:06.230
you shouldn't have been so ruthless.

14:07.060 --> 14:07.920
Presumptuous!

14:09.680 --> 14:11.130
Princess Fu is poisoned,

14:11.390 --> 14:13.280
and instead of staying at your manor
to save her,

14:13.280 --> 14:16.030
you broke into the palace late at night
to reprimand me

14:16.030 --> 14:17.750
and spout such nonsense.

14:20.550 --> 14:22.550
Please forgive my offense, Mother.

14:22.750 --> 14:23.880
But please, Mother,

14:24.960 --> 14:26.030
let go of Fu.

14:26.510 --> 14:27.440
Yan Qing.

14:29.600 --> 14:30.400
Your Majesty.

14:31.120 --> 14:32.550
Go summon Lord Zhan.

14:33.480 --> 14:35.870
Have him accompany the Crown Prince
back to the manor

14:35.870 --> 14:38.590
to investigate Princess Fu's poisoning.

14:41.400 --> 14:41.990
Yes.

14:51.770 --> 14:52.770
Your Highness,

14:53.100 --> 14:54.920
I have come by Her Majesty's decree

14:54.920 --> 14:57.470
to investigate the poisoning
of Princess Fu.

14:58.270 --> 15:00.070
Lord Zhan, what a grand display.

15:00.530 --> 15:02.240
Are you here to investigate the case,

15:02.240 --> 15:04.560
or to lay siege
to my Crown Prince's Mansion?

15:04.560 --> 15:06.130
The poisoning of Princess Fu

15:06.130 --> 15:07.660
is indeed a serious matter.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.770
If the poisoner is in the mansion,

15:10.350 --> 15:11.810
without strict guarding,

15:12.440 --> 15:14.100
they might escape at any time.

15:14.550 --> 15:16.480
I am only acting on the decree.

15:16.840 --> 15:18.370
Naturally, I must do my best

15:18.550 --> 15:20.600
and allow no room for error.

15:22.440 --> 15:24.270
Guard the Crown Prince's Mansion strictly.

15:24.270 --> 15:26.120
You must keep the Crown Prince safe

15:26.120 --> 15:28.120
and let no one in or out.

15:28.240 --> 15:29.000
Yes!

15:30.310 --> 15:31.190
Your Highness.

15:32.680 --> 15:36.220
Her Majesty specially requested
a palace physician to come here with us.

15:36.220 --> 15:38.550
Let us go see Princess Fu now.

15:50.150 --> 15:51.670
Keep a close eye on everything!

15:51.670 --> 15:53.070
Don't let anyone escape!

15:53.670 --> 15:54.390
Yes!

16:11.970 --> 16:13.870
Your Highness, did you mistakenly
take the wrong way

16:13.870 --> 16:14.840
in your haste?

16:15.200 --> 16:16.500
The study is on the left,

16:16.500 --> 16:19.300
and Princess Fu's bedroom
is on the right, I think.

16:19.990 --> 16:22.420
Lord Zhan, are you more familiar with

16:22.440 --> 16:24.500
the Crown Prince's Mansion than I am?

16:24.670 --> 16:26.400
I just have a good memory.

16:26.570 --> 16:28.770
I've been here before, so I know the way.

16:47.980 --> 16:50.380
No entry without the Crown Prince's order.

16:54.480 --> 16:55.210
How dare you!

16:56.780 --> 16:57.350
Move!

16:58.150 --> 16:58.910
Zhan Ziyu,

16:59.310 --> 17:01.910
how dare you
break into Princess Fu's bedroom!

17:02.630 --> 17:03.630
Your Highness,

17:04.349 --> 17:06.920
you claimed that Princess Fu was poisoned

17:07.240 --> 17:10.569
and went to the palace late at night
to question Her Majesty,

17:11.069 --> 17:13.810
but now you're trying to stop us
from checking on her.

17:13.810 --> 17:16.000
Are you trying to hide something?

17:18.480 --> 17:21.270
Or was Princess Fu not poisoned at all?

17:24.240 --> 17:25.240
Assassins!

17:30.210 --> 17:31.490
Don't run! Don't run!

17:42.640 --> 17:43.750
A female assassin?

17:44.680 --> 17:45.760
Get her!

17:46.100 --> 17:47.580
Don't let her escape.

17:54.350 --> 17:55.310
After her!

17:55.590 --> 17:57.030
No matter what it takes,

17:57.030 --> 17:58.160
you must find her!

17:58.160 --> 17:58.720
Stop!

18:00.110 --> 18:00.790
My Lord,

18:00.810 --> 18:02.340
the physician says
Princess Fu's poisoning is severe.

18:02.340 --> 18:03.870
He asked you to check on her.

18:19.110 --> 18:20.110
Didn't you bring a physician

18:20.110 --> 18:21.350
to treat Princess Fu?

18:21.830 --> 18:23.920
Weren't you going to
break into her bedroom?

18:23.920 --> 18:26.650
Why are you saying
there's nothing you can do now?

18:41.480 --> 18:42.400
Your Highness.

18:44.110 --> 18:45.040
What's going on?

18:46.200 --> 18:47.160
Forgive me, Your Highness.

18:47.160 --> 18:48.420
Forgive me, Lord Zhan.

18:48.590 --> 18:49.840
This poison is fierce.

18:49.840 --> 18:51.270
It's no ordinary poison.

18:51.750 --> 18:52.920
I really can't find a way

18:52.920 --> 18:55.030
to neutralize the poison right away.

18:55.250 --> 18:57.030
I can only write a prescription.

18:57.030 --> 18:59.650
Her Highness
will have to endure the pain for now,

18:59.650 --> 19:01.960
taking the medicine for 10 days,
after which

19:01.960 --> 19:04.360
the poison will naturally lose its effect.

19:09.590 --> 19:10.700
Ten days?

19:11.160 --> 19:13.680
You want Princess Fu
to endure this for 10 days?

19:13.680 --> 19:14.470
Useless!

19:15.240 --> 19:17.100
Don't be anxious, Your Highness.

19:17.400 --> 19:18.660
Since it's poisoning,

19:18.830 --> 19:20.560
it won't be cured in a day or two.

19:22.680 --> 19:24.440
Rather than giving the physician
a hard time,

19:24.440 --> 19:26.590
it would be better
to let him prepare the medicine,

19:26.590 --> 19:29.550
so that the Princess
can get some relief sooner.

19:29.920 --> 19:31.170
Hurry up and prepare the medicine.

19:31.170 --> 19:31.760
Yes.

19:42.030 --> 19:42.880
Lord Zhan,

19:43.350 --> 19:45.680
do you want to watch Princess Fu recover

19:45.920 --> 19:47.400
in person?

19:50.110 --> 19:51.720
I have no intention of offending.

19:51.720 --> 19:52.750
I will leave now.

19:53.960 --> 19:56.000
I'll let Her Highness have some quiet time
to recuperate.

19:56.000 --> 19:56.660
Song Cheng.

19:56.830 --> 19:57.400
Yes.

19:58.510 --> 19:59.640
See Lord Zhan out.

20:14.110 --> 20:14.790
Qiao!

20:15.510 --> 20:16.000
Hurry!

20:16.310 --> 20:17.590
Get the antidote for me!

20:17.590 --> 20:18.030
Okay.

20:22.840 --> 20:23.600
Is this it?

20:31.000 --> 20:31.860
How do you feel?

20:33.310 --> 20:35.310
How could you actually take poison?

20:35.920 --> 20:36.640
I'm fine.

20:37.240 --> 20:39.000
When I was in Qingshan Manor,

20:39.350 --> 20:40.970
I carried this Gelsemium with me

20:40.970 --> 20:43.100
just in case.

20:49.640 --> 20:50.200
Come on.

20:54.790 --> 20:55.650
How do you feel?

20:56.070 --> 20:57.130
Is the poison gone?

20:57.880 --> 20:58.920
I'm fine now.

20:59.550 --> 21:01.070
When I was a spy,

21:01.070 --> 21:04.140
I often tested and neutralized poisons
to identify them.

21:04.140 --> 21:06.540
A little time like this
won't do me any harm.

21:07.270 --> 21:08.030
That's good.

21:09.240 --> 21:10.000
However...

21:10.200 --> 21:12.390
Zhan Ziyu's men
were all over the mansion just now.

21:12.390 --> 21:13.520
How did you get back?

21:23.680 --> 21:24.510
Minglu?

21:24.830 --> 21:26.490
You haven't fully recovered,

21:26.520 --> 21:28.640
but you dared to come alone to kill him.

21:28.640 --> 21:29.900
If this isn't suicide,

21:30.110 --> 21:30.960
what is?

21:31.070 --> 21:32.270
Then why are you here?

21:32.830 --> 21:34.030
Don't flatter yourself.

21:34.030 --> 21:35.360
I'm not here to help you.

21:35.960 --> 21:38.830
Muhe Xifeng and Zhao Kuo were among those

21:39.920 --> 21:43.620
who killed my father
and his brother back then.

21:43.640 --> 21:44.470
Don't kill me!

21:45.070 --> 21:46.030
Chu Qiao!

21:46.510 --> 21:47.750
I'm not lying to you!

21:47.770 --> 21:49.410
I really have information
to exchange with you.

21:49.410 --> 21:52.000
Your vice commander
of the Xiuli Army, He Xiao,

21:52.000 --> 21:53.460
didn't die at Meilin Pass.

21:53.960 --> 21:56.360
He was just captured
and forced into labor.

21:56.810 --> 21:57.410
Tell me!

21:57.750 --> 21:58.880
Where is He Xiao?

21:58.920 --> 21:59.880
I don't know.

22:00.470 --> 22:01.640
If you don't tell me,

22:02.400 --> 22:04.800
I will cut off your hands and feet
one by one.

22:04.960 --> 22:06.760
I've told you everything I know.

22:06.960 --> 22:08.830
You... you can't kill me.

22:09.240 --> 22:09.960
Chu Qiao,

22:10.920 --> 22:12.030
we're even now.

22:12.550 --> 22:13.240
Okay.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.030
We're even now.

22:14.030 --> 22:14.790
Yes, we are.

22:31.480 --> 22:32.150
Minglu.

22:33.440 --> 22:34.070
It's me.

22:42.110 --> 22:42.720
Qiao!

22:51.350 --> 22:53.000
Zhan Ziyu's men are gone now,

22:53.400 --> 22:55.590
but he's sure you can't escape the city,

22:55.590 --> 22:57.790
so he might search this area for a while.

22:58.030 --> 22:59.430
You can hide here for now.

22:59.660 --> 23:01.070
I don't need you to do this.

23:01.070 --> 23:02.110
I can't kill you,

23:02.400 --> 23:04.070
and I can't avenge my father.

23:04.680 --> 23:06.030
I might as well die.

23:10.570 --> 23:12.070
You're even afraid of pain,

23:12.070 --> 23:14.200
and you say you're not afraid of death?

23:17.510 --> 23:18.270
Don't move.

23:19.190 --> 23:20.590
It's just been bandaged.

23:23.070 --> 23:23.720
Qiao,

23:24.720 --> 23:26.790
this is an old restaurant I bought.

23:27.050 --> 23:27.940
It's empty,

23:28.160 --> 23:30.090
and nobody knows about this place.

23:35.070 --> 23:35.750
Take it.

23:37.000 --> 23:38.400
Rest here for a while.

23:38.720 --> 23:41.400
Come back and kill me when you're healed.

23:58.070 --> 23:58.870
Your Majesty.

23:59.440 --> 24:00.750
Physician Liu has examined her.

24:00.750 --> 24:02.930
She really has been poisoned by Gelsemium.

24:02.930 --> 24:04.680
There shouldn't be any mistake.

24:04.680 --> 24:07.240
There might be more to this.

24:10.400 --> 24:11.200
Your Majesty,

24:11.270 --> 24:13.640
Zhao Kuo was assassinated on the road.

24:20.440 --> 24:21.240
Your Majesty,

24:21.590 --> 24:22.450
what happened?

24:23.000 --> 24:25.660
Just now, Zhao Kuo
was assassinated on the road.

24:30.310 --> 24:31.770
Princess Fu was poisoned,

24:32.110 --> 24:33.350
and Lord Zhao was killed.

24:33.350 --> 24:35.640
Aren't these two things
too much of a coincidence?

24:35.640 --> 24:37.030
You think it's

24:37.680 --> 24:38.920
just a coincidence?

24:40.270 --> 24:42.130
Could it be that Lord Zhao's death

24:42.200 --> 24:43.920
is related to the Crown Prince?

24:43.920 --> 24:45.880
Didn't the Crown Prince come to the palace
and make such a scene

24:45.880 --> 24:47.880
just to show me clearly

24:48.350 --> 24:50.360
that they had nothing to do with this?

24:50.360 --> 24:51.690
There is one more thing.

24:52.920 --> 24:53.850
Because of this,

24:54.270 --> 24:55.310
the Crown Prince

24:56.070 --> 24:57.960
has expelled all the spies

24:58.270 --> 25:00.000
we sent into his mansion.

25:00.720 --> 25:01.510
Ce,

25:03.270 --> 25:05.870
your act
of pretending to be absurd and foolish

25:05.900 --> 25:07.730
was very convincing.

25:35.400 --> 25:36.350
This contains the second thing

25:36.350 --> 25:37.880
King Ximeng wants you to do.

25:38.240 --> 25:39.770
You will stay here for today

25:40.350 --> 25:42.080
and set off from here tomorrow.

25:44.840 --> 25:45.440
Oh, right.

25:46.110 --> 25:47.480
Remember to change

25:48.270 --> 25:49.070
your clothes.

25:56.570 --> 25:59.390
[Imperial City]

26:35.590 --> 26:39.250
When someone makes a mistake,
they should naturally be punished.

26:42.160 --> 26:43.270
I failed in my duty,

26:43.920 --> 26:46.160
allowing Zhuge Yue to hurt Your Majesty.

26:46.160 --> 26:47.960
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

26:48.000 --> 26:49.640
You are a useful slave.

26:50.110 --> 26:51.310
I still need you.

26:51.920 --> 26:53.550
But they are different.

26:56.110 --> 26:56.960
You are right.

26:57.590 --> 26:58.920
Then let me do it myself.

27:20.570 --> 27:21.270
Enough!

27:22.830 --> 27:24.500
I don't like losers.

27:25.240 --> 27:26.500
If there is a next time,

27:26.680 --> 27:29.170
they won't die so easily.

27:51.900 --> 27:53.450
For this trip to Biantang,

27:53.480 --> 27:54.970
you have two missions.

27:55.200 --> 27:57.030
First, you must be around

27:57.030 --> 27:59.200
this fake King Ximeng all the time.

27:59.440 --> 28:01.000
By any means necessary,

28:01.160 --> 28:02.380
bring back the person I want

28:02.380 --> 28:04.790
along with his records.

28:05.270 --> 28:06.680
Besides you,

28:06.920 --> 28:08.070
his true identity

28:08.070 --> 28:10.200
must remain a secret to everyone else.

28:10.240 --> 28:10.720
Yes.

28:10.930 --> 28:13.690
Second, Zhuge Yue is unpredictable

28:13.720 --> 28:14.890
and cunning.

28:15.270 --> 28:17.800
You must stay on guard against him
all the way.

28:18.270 --> 28:19.960
Once his mission is complete,

28:20.310 --> 28:22.270
kill him in Biantang.

28:22.750 --> 28:24.070
Whatever it takes,

28:24.070 --> 28:25.530
do not let him leave there.

28:25.790 --> 28:27.250
Otherwise, in the future,

28:27.790 --> 28:30.720
he will become a great threat to us.

28:54.030 --> 28:54.680
Who is it?

28:55.580 --> 28:56.730
Is Princess Fu here?

29:05.610 --> 29:09.710
[Zi Ming, Li Ce's Concubine]

29:08.680 --> 29:09.590
Princess Fu,

29:09.790 --> 29:11.510
I came specifically to see you.

29:11.510 --> 29:12.720
His Highness told me to avoid you

29:12.720 --> 29:14.160
and stay out of your sight,

29:14.160 --> 29:16.000
but I thought you wouldn't mind.

29:16.170 --> 29:18.490
So I took the liberty
of coming to see you.

29:19.030 --> 29:20.480
I thought that after last night,

29:20.480 --> 29:22.240
with the palace people causing a ruckus,

29:22.240 --> 29:23.590
breaking into your room,

29:23.590 --> 29:25.240
and even trying to poison you,

29:25.240 --> 29:27.240
you must be starving and exhausted.

29:27.720 --> 29:28.680
So I made some dishes

29:28.680 --> 29:30.310
and snacks

29:30.400 --> 29:31.720
for you to try.

29:42.510 --> 29:45.160
Have some tea to moisten your throat
before you eat.

29:45.160 --> 29:47.220
It's good for your digestive system.

30:10.240 --> 30:10.920
How is it?

30:15.000 --> 30:15.640
It's good.

30:19.480 --> 30:21.200
Zi Ming, why are you here?

30:24.960 --> 30:25.550
Fu,

30:26.030 --> 30:27.920
Zi Ming is not a spy sent by Mother,

30:28.250 --> 30:29.980
so I kept her here.

30:33.000 --> 30:33.860
Your Highness,

30:33.880 --> 30:36.460
I saw you practicing swordsmanship
in the courtyard the other day.

30:36.460 --> 30:37.460
It was beautiful.

30:38.000 --> 30:39.860
Could you teach me some other day?

30:56.510 --> 30:57.830
What's going on today?

30:58.030 --> 30:59.850
His Majesty doesn't even attend
the morning court usually.

30:59.850 --> 31:00.560
Why did he suddenly

31:00.560 --> 31:02.760
summon us to the afternoon court today?

31:03.310 --> 31:05.440
I heard it's related to Ximeng.

31:05.720 --> 31:07.310
The day before yesterday, the Ximeng envoy

31:07.310 --> 31:08.960
delivered a diplomatic note.

31:08.960 --> 31:10.640
I wonder what it is about.

31:10.640 --> 31:11.550
Ximeng?

31:11.750 --> 31:13.160
We have no interactions with Ximeng.

31:13.160 --> 31:14.560
What are they doing here?

31:14.710 --> 31:15.440
I don't know.

31:16.350 --> 31:18.160
Grand Secretary Liu
has been on sick leave for days.

31:18.160 --> 31:19.690
Why hasn't he returned yet?

31:20.310 --> 31:20.640
Well...

31:20.640 --> 31:22.440
Lord Liu is hiding from trouble.

31:26.530 --> 31:28.590
The Emperor asked him to assist
the Crown Prince in governing the state.

31:28.590 --> 31:30.240
He thinks it's a tough job,

31:29.770 --> 31:33.720
[Sun Di, General of Cavalry of Biantang]

31:31.570 --> 31:33.650
so he's feigning illness at home.

31:35.640 --> 31:37.720
General Sun, you're straightforward,

31:37.720 --> 31:40.200
but this is not the right place to talk.

31:40.550 --> 31:41.610
What am I afraid of?

31:42.590 --> 31:44.910
Everyone knows
the Crown Prince is a lost cause.

31:44.910 --> 31:47.350
If His Majesty had other sons
of the right age,

31:47.350 --> 31:49.310
would he have stayed in this position
for so long?

31:49.310 --> 31:50.240
If you ask me,

31:51.310 --> 31:52.970
Grand Secretary Liu is right.

31:53.110 --> 31:54.110
If it were me,

31:55.720 --> 31:58.310
I would also feign illness
and skip the court.

32:10.110 --> 32:10.970
Your Highness,

32:11.280 --> 32:13.610
Her Majesty invites you to Fengyi Palace.

32:56.010 --> 32:58.010
Your Xiuli Army commander, He Xiao,

32:58.310 --> 32:59.480
is as tough as you.

32:59.830 --> 33:01.550
He didn't die in battle at Meilin Pass.

33:01.550 --> 33:03.950
He was just captured
and forced into labor.

33:10.680 --> 33:11.440
He Xiao,

33:13.250 --> 33:15.050
I will definitely take you home.

33:21.790 --> 33:23.830
Greetings, Mother.

33:24.510 --> 33:26.270
Mother, I apologize for being rude

33:26.270 --> 33:27.480
and disturbing you yesterday.

33:27.480 --> 33:29.350
About Princess Fu being poisoned,

33:29.350 --> 33:30.830
have you found out the truth?

33:30.830 --> 33:31.720
Not yet.

33:32.110 --> 33:33.720
But I believe it was those concubines,

33:33.720 --> 33:36.160
jealous of me and Princess Fu
being deeply in love,

33:36.160 --> 33:37.270
who poisoned her.

33:37.640 --> 33:38.590
I was reckless

33:38.880 --> 33:40.680
and misunderstood you, Mother.

33:40.880 --> 33:42.410
Please forgive me, Mother.

33:42.720 --> 33:43.920
How is Princess Fu?

33:44.200 --> 33:45.790
Thank you for your concern, Mother.

33:45.790 --> 33:46.850
She is much better.

33:47.400 --> 33:50.000
But the envoy from Great Yong
is not doing well.

33:50.400 --> 33:51.800
He was killed yesterday,

33:52.750 --> 33:54.270
right outside Tangjing.

33:54.480 --> 33:55.110
What?

33:55.960 --> 33:57.690
The envoy of Great Yong is dead?

34:03.880 --> 34:04.510
Ce,

34:05.000 --> 34:06.760
do you know who told me

34:07.400 --> 34:09.280
that Princess Fu is Chu Qiao?

34:09.840 --> 34:12.280
It was this Great Yong envoy, Zhao Kuo.

34:13.230 --> 34:14.889
It's a pity that he's dead now.

34:14.940 --> 34:17.340
No one
will ever suspect Princess Fu again.

34:28.400 --> 34:30.630
Don't you agree, Ce?

34:31.800 --> 34:32.429
Mother,

34:33.280 --> 34:35.150
who killed the Great Yong envoy?

34:35.880 --> 34:36.840
Are there any clues?

34:36.840 --> 34:38.239
Now that Zhao Kuo is dead,

34:38.679 --> 34:41.370
Great Yong will definitely demand
an explanation from us.

34:41.370 --> 34:43.300
But this has nothing to do with you.

34:43.670 --> 34:44.440
You can still

34:44.440 --> 34:46.440
be deeply in love with your Princess Fu

34:46.440 --> 34:47.500
and live your life.

34:48.030 --> 34:49.000
Not only that.

34:49.320 --> 34:50.360
Now, even

34:50.360 --> 34:51.840
the concubines I gave you

34:52.070 --> 34:53.190
have made mistakes

34:53.440 --> 34:56.000
and brought it upon themselves
to be kicked out.

34:56.000 --> 34:57.960
From now on, let alone Princess Fu,

34:58.760 --> 35:01.000
even if you keep the real Chu Qiao
in your mansion,

35:01.000 --> 35:02.440
no one will know.

35:03.000 --> 35:05.030
If you really had Chu Qiao,

35:05.280 --> 35:07.070
not only could it cause
Great Yan and Great Yong

35:07.070 --> 35:09.270
to use it as an opportunity to attack us,

35:09.550 --> 35:12.880
you could also use Chu Qiao
to build a private army and rebel.

35:13.180 --> 35:15.730
Didn't Heir Apparent Yan
join forces with her back then

35:15.730 --> 35:17.650
and march all the way to Zhenhuang City,

35:17.650 --> 35:20.180
catching the Emperor of Great Yong
off guard?

35:22.400 --> 35:22.880
Mother.

35:23.510 --> 35:24.670
As the Crown Prince,

35:24.960 --> 35:27.360
although I lack the virtue and talent
to share the burden of Father and you,

35:27.360 --> 35:29.510
I would never do such an absurd thing.

35:30.110 --> 35:32.070
I truly like Fu.

35:32.070 --> 35:33.480
I was afraid that she would be angry,

35:33.480 --> 35:34.280
so I made an excuse

35:34.280 --> 35:36.840
to kick those beautiful concubines
out of the mansion.

35:36.840 --> 35:38.590
I've been lacking in ability
since I was young.

35:38.590 --> 35:40.320
Thanks to your doting
and protection, Mother,

35:40.320 --> 35:42.250
I was able to survive in the palace.

35:42.360 --> 35:43.960
At the afternoon court today,

35:43.960 --> 35:45.510
I'm about to tell Father

35:45.920 --> 35:48.190
that I cannot take on the great responsibility
of governing the state.

35:48.190 --> 35:50.250
I will ask him to allow you to continue

35:50.360 --> 35:52.960
bearing this heavy burden for me.

36:02.960 --> 36:03.920
Rise, Ce.

36:05.440 --> 36:06.030
Yes.

36:13.920 --> 36:14.510
Ce,

36:15.360 --> 36:17.480
since you are the Crown Prince
of a country,

36:17.480 --> 36:19.070
how can you easily shirk

36:19.230 --> 36:20.530
the heavy responsibility
of governing the state?

36:20.530 --> 36:22.590
I only secured
this position of Crown Prince

36:22.590 --> 36:24.520
because of your prestige, Mother.

36:24.710 --> 36:25.770
To govern the state

36:25.920 --> 36:28.400
is to shoulder the responsibility
for the people.

36:28.400 --> 36:30.260
I have neither talent nor virtue.

36:30.440 --> 36:33.440
Please keep helping me
bear this burden, Mother.

36:46.810 --> 36:47.610
-Qiao.
-Li Ce.

36:49.090 --> 36:51.490
-I have something...
-I have something...

36:51.920 --> 36:53.520
-You go first.
-You go first.

36:54.030 --> 36:55.550
Alright, I'll go first.

36:56.400 --> 36:57.880
That day, I heard some news

36:58.030 --> 36:59.190
from Zhao Kuo.

36:59.840 --> 37:01.840
He Xiao is still alive.

37:02.230 --> 37:03.290
He is in Great Yong.

37:03.400 --> 37:04.820
I want you to help me find out

37:04.820 --> 37:06.080
where he is being held.

37:06.320 --> 37:07.450
I want to rescue him.

37:08.880 --> 37:11.000
I also have a favor to ask of you.

37:13.590 --> 37:15.650
Qiao, do you remember telling me that

37:16.000 --> 37:17.000
once you recover,

37:17.400 --> 37:18.960
you would not only protect me,

37:18.960 --> 37:21.090
but also help me take back what is mine?

37:23.030 --> 37:24.030
Get up first.

37:25.880 --> 37:26.510
Li Ce,

37:27.550 --> 37:28.440
you want...

37:28.460 --> 37:29.900
I want to reclaim

37:30.880 --> 37:32.320
my power from my mother.

37:32.880 --> 37:33.440
Qiao,

37:33.880 --> 37:35.150
although I am the Crown Prince,

37:35.150 --> 37:36.230
I can only live under the shadow

37:36.230 --> 37:37.550
of my mother's power.

37:37.790 --> 37:39.550
You were once the martial arts instructor
of Great Yong's imperial guard,

37:39.550 --> 37:40.730
and you led the Xiuli Army.

37:40.730 --> 37:41.810
I will provide the money and resources,

37:41.810 --> 37:43.840
and I want you
to train a secret army for me.

37:43.840 --> 37:45.790
This army will be mine in the future.

37:45.790 --> 37:47.640
At the same time, I will help you find out

37:47.640 --> 37:49.150
news about He Xiao in Great Yong.

37:49.150 --> 37:51.000
This way, given time,

37:51.230 --> 37:52.630
once this army is formed,

37:52.880 --> 37:54.310
you can also use it to help you

37:54.310 --> 37:56.040
rescue He Xiao from Great Yong.

38:02.150 --> 38:03.360
Well played, Li Ce.

38:04.070 --> 38:05.920
Not only do you want
to make a deal with me,

38:05.920 --> 38:07.610
but you also want to tie me down to you?

38:07.610 --> 38:09.490
How is this tying you down, Qiao?

38:10.230 --> 38:11.630
You are a female general.

38:11.630 --> 38:14.160
You must take responsibility
for your words.

38:17.110 --> 38:19.150
I can't spend my whole life
playing the role of

38:19.150 --> 38:22.110
a loser indulging in luxury
and debauchery.

38:22.920 --> 38:24.460
I must first be able to protect myself,

38:24.460 --> 38:27.190
so that I can protect the people
I want to protect.

38:57.170 --> 39:00.370
Didn't you see that the dancer
His Majesty kept staring at

39:00.380 --> 39:02.420
looked a bit like Chu Qiao?

39:02.450 --> 39:04.510
Our Biantang has prepared a state banquet

39:04.510 --> 39:06.550
to welcome King Ximeng.

39:08.480 --> 39:10.510
But I'm afraid in King Ximeng's eyes,

39:10.510 --> 39:12.720
there is no one worthy of his trust.

39:13.490 --> 39:14.130
Xing?
